OL,3,CDeputy-elect Le Brun tops the polls
OL,4,Cwith 953 votes
OL,6,FThe results were announced at midnight
OL,7,Ftonight (29 April) and are as follows:
OL,9,FRoss Le Brun: 953 votes
OL,11,FCarl Meerveld: 891 votes
OL,13,FJulie-Anne Headington: 634 votes
OL,15,FTamara Menteshvili: 440 votes
OL,17,FSam Haskins: 407 votes
OL,19,FAndy Taylor: 388 votes
OL,21,FNikki Symons: 371 votes
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
