OL,3,CDeputy-elect Le Brun tops the polls
OL,4,Cwith 953 votes
OL,6,FStephen Rouxel: 230 votes
OL,8,FJonathan Wilson: 162 votes
OL,10,FLuke Graham: 88 votes
OL,12,FRob Harnish: 79 votes
OL,14,FRoss Le Brun
OL,16,FThis isn't the first time Mr Le Brun
OL,17,Fhas tried to get into the States, most
OL,18,Frecently standing in the 2025 election.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
