PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1777558269
OL,3,CDeputy-elect Le Brun tops the polls
OL,4,Cwith 953 votes
OL,6,FHe also spent four and half years as a
OL,7,Fnon-voting member on Employment and
OL,8,FSocial Security.
OL,10,FWhen asked why he was standing he said:
OL,12,F"I did not come from a financially
OL,13,Fcomfortable background or well-
OL,14,Fconnected network. I grew up in social
OL,15,Fhousing, and my path has been built on
OL,16,Fhard work, determination, and
OL,17,Funderstanding the real challenges many
OL,18,Fpeople in our community face.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1777558269
OL,3,CDeputy-elect Le Brun tops the polls
OL,4,Cwith 953 votes
OL,6,F"I started my own business, growing it
OL,7,Fto employ nearly 400 local people over
OL,8,Ftime. That experience has given me a
OL,9,Fpractical understanding of jobs, the
OL,10,Feconomy, and what it takes to create
OL,11,Fopportunities for others.
OL,13,F"I am the only candidate who chose to
OL,14,Fserve on ESS to be able to work on
OL,15,Faffordable housing. I did the full
OL,16,F4.5yrs as a non voting member tackling
OL,17,Fone of the island's most pressing
OL,18,Fissues."
OL,20,FIn response to the announcement
OL,21,Ftonight he told ITV:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1777558269
OL,3,CDeputy-elect Le Brun tops the polls
OL,4,Cwith 953 votes
OL,6,F"I'm glad this part of the process is
OL,7,Fover, but it's just one battle and now
OL,8,Fthe work continues. I've now got a
OL,9,Fburden on my shoulders and an
OL,10,Fexpectation that I've given people
OL,11,Fthat I can get things done."
OL,13,FVoter Turnout
OL,15,FAs expected the turnout for this
OL,16,Fyear's by-election was much lower than
OL,17,Fthe Island Wide Election last year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
